title: Ep - 76 - TINSLEY MORTIMER
description:
Tinsley Mortimer from Real Housewives of New York discusses her pre-Bravo life including her 2010 show High Society. She opens up about experience with domestic abuse and gives an update on her romance with Scott Kluth. 


Steven Stauff, a father of four in Orange County, California, reviews an episode of Real Estate Wars on Bravo. 


Podcast host Cheri Armour Samples chats about this season of Don’t Be Tardy.
